        "description": "Get a single invoice by its ID. Returns the invoice record including `invoiceNumber`, `dueDate`, `reference`, computed totals, and a presigned S3 URL to download the PDF.\n\n**Path variable:**\n- `invoiceId` (Long): The ID of the invoice\n\n```bash\ncurl -X GET \"{{base_url}}/api/v1/estimates/invoices/1\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}\"\n```"
